description:
It’s time to become a football star and to win your first American football match but first you’d better start your trainings.

American Football Match is a running game with numerous obstacles. Run as fast as you can, don’t let anyone stop you. Your opponents will definitely try to knock you down so be careful and react quickly! Gridiron football is such a rough sports game! Be a football star and have fun playing gridiron football!

Beware as the other players differ one from another by uniform’s color. Just avoid them and don’t drop the ball!

- Captivating yet simple running game;
- Unlock new cool or funny sports uniform;
- Get ready for a gridiron football match by training in our running game!
